{"tid":407390,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"三級片香港票房排行榜","createTime":"2017-09-20T11:41:24.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-21T09:50:21.000Z","uid":134071,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"caa88b90cfd4fd351b474c9a62395166af5e7b44","tid":407390,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T11:41:24.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><a href=\"http://thestandnews.com/culture/%E4%B8%89%E7%B4%9A%E7%89%87%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E7%A5%A8%E6%88%BF%E6%8E%92%E8%A1%8C%E6%A6%9C/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fculture%2F%25E4%25B8%2589%25E7%25B4%259A%25E7%2589%2587%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E7%25A5%25A8%25E6%2588%25BF%25E6%258E%2592%25E8%25A1%258C%25E6%25A6%259C%2F&d=6dZpwG%2FIIOfku5N8VV850i7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=44111463\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fculture%2F%25E4%25B8%2589%25E7%25B4%259A%25E7%2589%2587%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E7%25A5%25A8%25E6%2588%25BF%25E6%258E%2592%25E8%25A1%258C%25E6%25A6%259C%2F&h=630d95ed\" target=\"_blank\">http://thestandnews.com/culture/%E4%B8%89%E7%B4%9A%E7%89%87%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E7%A5%A8%E6%88%BF%E6%8E%92%E8%A1%8C%E6%A6%9C/</a></span><br />\n<br />\n三級片香港票房排行榜<br />\n<br />\n2017/9/19 &mdash; 18:20<br />\n<br />\n【文：Chun Kong】<br />\n<br />\n下表為2017年9月的更新<br />\n<br />\n由於觀眾年齡限制，如果一套三級片在香港戲院票房能超過1000萬港元，基本上已算十分理想了 (由1988年三級制實行以來, 香港戲院票房能超過1000萬港元的三級片, 不足55套.) 以下是小弟一直以來為所有香港戲院票房能超過1000萬港元的三級片特製的票房排行榜. 這次在2017年9月的更新，加上了《盧根》, 《格雷的五十道色戒2》, 《雛妓》等電影。(資料來源credit在文章尾段)<br />\n<br />\n01) 《死侍：不死現身》（DEADPOOL） [2016] &ndash; 5833萬（影片的三級版本和二B級版本是同時在香港戲院上映，此票房數字是所有版本的戲院票房的總和）<br />\n02) 《色,戒》（Lust, Caution）[2007] - 4875萬<br />\n03) 《3D肉蒲團之極樂寶鑑》[2011] - 4107萬<br />\n04)《盧根》（Logan） [2017] - 3854萬<br />\n05)《華爾街狼人》(The Wolf of Wall Street) [2014] - 3110萬<br />\n06)《低俗喜劇》[2012] - 3006萬 (多謝網友更正）<br />\n07)《本能》 （Basic Instinct）[1992] &ndash; 2779萬<br />\n08)《失蹤罪》 （Gone Girl）[2014] &ndash; 2271萬<br />\n09)《那夜凌晨，我坐上了旺角開往大埔的紅Van》 [2014] &ndash; 2129萬（影片的三級版本和二B級版本是同時在香港戲院上映，此票房數字是所有版本的戲院票房的總和）<br />\n10)《一路向西》[2012] - 1925萬<br />\n11)《艷舞女郎》（Showgirls）[1995] - 1891萬<br />\n12)《玉蒲團之偷情寶鑑》[1991] - 1842萬<br />\n13)《雛妓》[2015] - 1743萬<br />\n14)《殭屍》[2013] &ndash;1716萬 （影片的三級版本和二B級版本是同時在香港戲院上映，此票房數字是所有版本的戲院票房的總和）<br />\n15)《飛虎出征》[2013] &ndash; 1674萬<br />\n16)《3D豪情》 [2014] &ndash; 1607萬<br />\n17)《黑社會》[2005] &ndash; 1589萬<br />\n18)《色慾都市》（Sex and the City） [2008] &ndash; 1588萬<br />\n19)《97古惑仔:戰無不勝》[1997] &ndash; 1579萬 （影片最初在香港戲院上映二B級版本， 後來改為上映三級版本，此票房數字是所有版本的戲院票房的總和）<br />\n20)《八仙飯店之人肉叉燒包》[1993] &ndash; 1576萬<br />\n21)《受難曲》（The Passion of the Christ）[2004] &ndash; 1546萬<br />\n22)《情人》 （The Lover）[1992] &ndash; 1487萬<br />\n23)《格雷的五十道色戒2》（Fifty Shades Darker）[2017] &ndash; 1432萬<br />\n24)《我在黑社會的日子》 [1989] &ndash; 1403萬<br />\n25)《情不自禁》 [1991] &ndash; 1361萬<br />\n26)《黑社會:以和為貴》 [2006] &ndash; 1357萬<br />\n27)《滅門慘案之孽殺》 [1993] &ndash; 1327萬<br />\n28)《羔羊醫生》 [1992] &ndash; 1275萬<br />\n29)《美麗有罪》 （American Beauty）[2000] &ndash; 1254萬<br />\n30)《格雷的五十道色戒》（Fifty Shades of Grey）[2015] &ndash; 1233萬<br />\n31)《李麗珍 - 蜜桃成熟時》 [1993] - 1231萬<br />\n32)《香港奇案之強姦》 [1993] &ndash; 1195萬<br />\n33)《廟街皇后》[1990] &ndash; 1182萬<br />\n34)《色情男女》[1996] &ndash; 1161萬<br />\n35)《PARTY冇限耆》（Dirty Grandpa）[2016] &ndash; 1134萬<br />\n36)《聊齋艷譚》 [1990] &ndash; 1128萬<br />\n37)《死神4來了》（The Final Destination） [2009] &ndash; 1119萬（影片的三級版本和二B級版本是同時在香港戲院上映，此票房數字是所有版本的戲院票房的總和）<br />\n38)《告白》 [2010] &ndash; 1111萬<br />\n39)《神探》 [2007] -1109萬<br />\n40)《黑太陽731》 [1988] &ndash; 1109萬（影片最初在香港戲院上映三級版本，後來亦有上映二級版本，此票房數字是所有版本的戲院票房的總和--多謝網友更正）<br />\n41)《醉生夢死 之 灣仔之虎》[1994] &ndash; 1106萬<br />\n42)《聊齋艷譚續集:五通神》 [1991] &ndash; 1103萬<br />\n43)《三狼奇案》 [1989] &ndash; 1080萬<br />\n44)《偷窺》（Sliver）[1993] &ndash; 1073萬<br />\n45)《晚9朝5》[1994] &ndash; 1046萬<br />\n46)《三度誘惑》 [1990] &ndash;1044萬<br />\n47)《滿清十大酷刑》 [1994]-1040萬<br />\n48)《濠江風雲》 [1998] &ndash; 1030萬<br />\n49)《卿本佳人》 [1991] - 1026萬 （多謝網友更正）<br />\n50)《香港舞男》[1990] &ndash; 1024萬<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n資料來源主要來自：<br />\n<br />\n香港影業協會網站；<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://iha2005.web.fc2.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fiha2005.web.fc2.com&d=6dZpwG%2FIIOfku5N8VV850i7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=e8ee15a4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">iha2005.web.fc2.com</a>；<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkfilmart.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkfilmart.com&d=6dZpwG%2FIIOfku5N8VV850i7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=0de658a9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">hkfilmart.com</a>；<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://now.com.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnow.com.hk&d=6dZpwG%2FIIOfku5N8VV850i7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=94664cfd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">now.com.hk</a>；<br />\n<br />\n「講。鏟。片」；<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://boxofficemojo.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fboxofficemojo.com&d=6dZpwG%2FIIOfku5N8VV850i7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=0dceea34\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">boxofficemojo.com</a>；<br />\n<br />\n電影雙周刊 , [已故]<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://mov3.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmov3.com&d=6dZpwG%2FIIOfku5N8VV850i7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=751f9c63\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">mov3.com</a>；<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://tw.weibo.com/cinetel\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftw.weibo.com%2Fcinetel&d=6dZpwG%2FIIOfku5N8VV850i7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=c1d51873\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">tw.weibo.com/cinetel</a>"},{"pid":"d37927b5822f32303bd6815f44d1b3b221409a88","tid":407390,"uid":82532,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T11:49:37.000Z","msg":"3D肉蒲團都四千萬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc37a5114d20dec1bbf76afc51e4c7b212790489","tid":407390,"uid":10338,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T11:51:22.000Z","msg":"黑太陽咁多人睇<br />\n咁血腥恐怖都咁高票房<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50ea4f0806abc9360506e582c5c10adef62b6b4a","tid":407390,"uid":3185,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T14:53:03.000Z","msg":"《我在黑社會的日子》<br />\n呢套野我細個個陣行家見到個名，返到去寫左係幼稚園本功課上面<br />\n跟住比幼稚園校長捉左去傾左好耐偈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"114bda5aa9f025de491e6aba0f44e9c5a4a745cb","tid":407390,"uid":134071,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-21T02:43:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>《我在黑社會的日子》<br />\n呢套野我細個個陣行家見到個名，返到去寫左係幼稚園本功課上面<br />\n跟住比幼稚園校長捉左去傾左好耐偈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n套戲唔想三級, 係香港cut哂儀式鏡頭.... 結果都被列三級<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.dailymotion.com/video/x2p68qn\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.dailymotion.com%2Fvideo%2Fx2p68qn&d=6dZpwG%2FIIOfku5N8VV850i7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=634cc8b5\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.dailymotion.com/video/x2p68qn</a>"},{"pid":"c2ce408c31dd8798228cead9a20fb3e0a6aa5abd","tid":407390,"uid":60655,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-21T02:45:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>3D肉蒲團都四千萬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n因為大家都中撚晒伏"},{"pid":"980c8eef003584410223627322d9efddcb401730","tid":407390,"uid":53498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-21T02:45:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>黑太陽咁多人睇<br />\n咁血腥恐怖都咁高票房<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n煽動民族情緒不嬲都有市場"},{"pid":"e5fdd0e6e376d720e040339ce53d8a2064c75f59","tid":407390,"uid":38757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-21T02:51:37.000Z","msg":"千幾萬票房其實係九十年代黎講，算唔算收得？"},{"pid":"df7e93753fcd3d2f080e936df2035aa082ffa847","tid":407390,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-21T02:53:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>千幾萬票房其實係九十年代黎講，算唔算收得？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n三級片黎講, 算.... <br />\n<br />\n而家都算係 (高票價未必對票房有利: 身邊唔少人以前經常睇戲, 但後來都因為票價太高而唔再入戲院)"},{"pid":"a02c11afce7f707857d3eaa6df5105b2fd69c406","tid":407390,"uid":102096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-21T02:54:44.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"211f7ccc5f78188fb6e761dc3e0b1f8d634abfb9","tid":407390,"uid":51399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-21T02:57:59.000Z","msg":"宜家一百蚊張飛同以前五十蚊張飛都爭一倍啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5ecdb3e50eb99a17685ea3d59903ab038b5eb96","tid":407390,"uid":38757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-21T02:58:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>千幾萬票房其實係九十年代黎講，算唔算收得？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n三級片黎講, 算.... <br />\n<br />\n而家都算係 (高票價未必對票房有利: 身邊唔少人以前經常睇戲, 但後來都因為票價太高而唔再入戲院)</blockquote><br />\n我諗都係，三級制作成本唔知有無五百萬以上，有的的，其實都唔係好好賺...."},{"pid":"49ef4fb3a3081c529b68fc9cd8071857b055e6c6","tid":407390,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-21T02:59:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>宜家一百蚊張飛同以前五十蚊張飛都爭一倍啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n都因此流失了很多觀眾<br />\n<br />\n香港票價的提升, 跟香港觀眾消費力不成正比"},{"pid":"ed05a7c1680077a1b06fb780675635bf411b93f6","tid":407390,"uid":45650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-21T03:02:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>3D肉蒲團都四千萬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n因為大家都中撚晒伏</blockquote><br />\n個個為左雷凱欣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n老夫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b13f9ed2762efd9ede051df21b374c862e6cac35","tid":407390,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-21T03:03:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>千幾萬票房其實係九十年代黎講，算唔算收得？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n三級片黎講, 算.... <br />\n<br />\n而家都算係 (高票價未必對票房有利: 身邊唔少人以前經常睇戲, 但後來都因為票價太高而唔再入戲院)</blockquote><br />\n我諗都係，三級制作成本唔知有無五百萬以上，有的的，其實都唔係好好賺....</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n特別例子: 《玉蒲團之偷情寶鑑》用2000萬拍都大賺, 但嘉禾昆老燒話賺唔到錢, 老燒幾十年後先發現做左傻仔 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"226103665e6ea1ca375d66c50f33af8162c15520","tid":407390,"uid":44664,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-21T03:04:03.000Z","msg":"Logan咁少？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n真係估唔到"},{"pid":"fe6f29fb88018c036812836004eed1fa470cabde","tid":407390,"uid":38757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-21T03:06:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>千幾萬票房其實係九十年代黎講，算唔算收得？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n三級片黎講, 算.... <br />\n<br />\n而家都算係 (高票價未必對票房有利: 身邊唔少人以前經常睇戲, 但後來都因為票價太高而唔再入戲院)</blockquote><br />\n我諗都係，三級制作成本唔知有無五百萬以上，有的的，其實都唔係好好賺....</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n特別例子: 《玉蒲團之偷情寶鑑》用2000萬拍都大賺, 但嘉禾昆老燒話賺唔到錢, 老燒幾十年後先發現做左傻仔 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n呢個岩，尾個幾十名，可能當時票房都未必好好，但依家睇番，都已經係叫收得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa9b8e981306833bef64ffd142ad57b91ec5144a","tid":407390,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-21T03:07:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Logan咁少？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n真係估唔到</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n算高了, 高過變形金剛新一集"},{"pid":"9f4bc079aa3014f5f0a673a3a55a5125d93ef92e","tid":407390,"uid":83328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"repl